Product Description

Fusion5 A90 128GB Laptop

Fusion5 is a leading independent brand selling tablet PCs since 2010. Fusion5 has served more than a million customers across the globe.

A90 128GB Windows 11 Laptop PC features 5 GHz WIFI which means the download and upload speeds are at least 2x faster than traditional laptops. Furthermore, our A90 128GB is designed such that it can handle complex tasks with ease. A90 128GB (v2) is 135% faster than our T90B+ pro (v1) according to benchmark tests.

Specification of A90 128GB Laptop:

Display 14.1" 1920*1080 Full HD
CPU Intel N4020 Chipset
External Storage Additional M.2 Slot
RAM/Memory 4 GB DDR4
Storage 128 GB
Camera 2MP
WIFI 802.11ac (5 GHz)
Operating system Windows 11
Input AC 100-240V 50-60Hz
Output DC 12V/3A
Battery 10000mAh 37Wh
Bluetooth 4.0

FEATURES:

TERRIFIC DOWNLOAD AND UPLOAD SPEEDS

Your new Lapbook comes with DDR4 4GB RAM and 128GB of onboard eMMC storage with the option to expand the memory up to 256GB with a Micro SD card (tf-card) or Insert an HDD (up to 1TB) and increase the internal storage immediately.

AMAZING VIEWER EXPERIENCE

This Fusion5 Laptop PC comes with an Amazing 14.1" 1920*1080 Full HD IPS display meaning you can now compute on the move in stunning Full HD and High resolution for the Ultimate portable Windows 11 notebook laptop experience.

SUPER LIGHT AND FLEXIBLE

Fusion5 A90B+ Pro New notebook laptop is light and easy to carry around weighing just 1346 grams. It also stretches to 170° and becomes totally flat if needed!

The laptop is backed with Windows 11.

Why a Fusion5 Product?

Fusion5 is a multi-award-winning brand focused on selling top-quality laptop & tablet PCs since 2010 which means we know what it takes to provide you with a fast, reliable, and versatile tech that supports your everyday life, your travels, and everything in between.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings, help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
